{"tid":1241080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線：換新身分證被徹選民身份？","createTime":"2019-06-18T14:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:39:26.000Z","uid":258055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5905d61052fedca94f60423e04d0fb818620b400","tid":1241080,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"【換新身份證被撤選民身份？】<br />\n【選舉事務處：入境處電腦出事遲交資料】<br />\n<br />\n市民正分批換領新的智能身份證，但有已換證的選民就發現，自己不在選民登記冊內。<br />\n選舉事務處解釋，是入境處電腦系統出問題，遲了轉交資料。<br />\n但據了解，入境處認為，有否傳送更新資料，與選民身份無關。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #選舉事務處 #入境處 #智能身份證 #選民 #登記 #翻查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1136633879862012/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1136633879862012%2F&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8EXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=55c0230a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1136633879862012/</a>"}]}